      "x": 500, "y": 90,
      "width": 230, "height": 100,
      "text": "InfoNCE Loss (τ=0.07)\n\n-log[exp(sim(z_a,z_pos)/τ)\n      / Σ_j exp(sim(z_a,z_j)/τ)]\n\nAll in-batch negatives used",
